# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# MCP Complete Guide — Environment Variables Template
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
#
# HOW TO USE:
#   1. Copy this file: cp .env.example .env
#   2. Fill in your values in .env
#   3. Never commit .env to Git (it's in .gitignore)
#
# WHICH KEYS DO YOU NEED?
#   • Basic examples (weather, calculator, files): NONE
#   • GitHub Agent: GITHUB_TOKEN
#   • Claude API Agent: ANTHROPIC_API_KEY
#   • Premium weather: WEATHER_API_KEY
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# ─── Anthropic / Claude ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Get from: https://console.anthropic.com
# Used by: examples/07_claude_integration/claude_api_agent.py
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-your-key-here

# ─── GitHub ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Get from: https://github.com/settings/tokens
# Scopes needed: repo, read:user
# Used by: projects/github_agent/github_agent.py
GITHUB_TOKEN=ghp_your_token_here

# ─── Weather API (Optional — free tier available) ──────────────────────────
# Get from: https://www.weatherapi.com (free tier: 1M calls/month)
# Used by: examples/08_advanced_agents/secure_production_server.py
# NOTE: Most weather examples use wttr.in which needs NO key
WEATHER_API_KEY=your_weather_api_key_here

# ─── Server Configuration ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
# These have sensible defaults — only change if needed
MCP_SERVER_NAME=my-mcp-server
LOG_LEVEL=INFO
MAX_TEXT_LENGTH=5000
REQUEST_TIMEOUT=15
RATE_LIMIT_CALLS=10
RATE_LIMIT_WINDOW=60
